            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-skelleftea"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "Skellefteå’s most popular crag. Routes in all grades, though unfortunately they are becoming overgrown with moss. The routes are spread across four small walls.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-skelleftea"
            ]
          }
        },
        "miljo": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Conditions",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-skelleftea"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "North-facing, but with solid rock. A good place to climb in midsummer. The Ingen utväg sector gets morning sun.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-skelleftea"
            ]
          }
        },
        "vagbeskrivning": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Directions",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-skelleftea"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "From the E4, turn towards Sörböle at the southern roundabout (E4 N, Anderstorp, E4 S and Sörböle). Follow the road to a slaughterhouse, where Falkträsket is signposted. Head towards Falkträsket. Continue past the bathing area and the holiday cottages. Then turn right onto a small forest road signposted Falkstugan. Park ‘behind’ the crag.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-skelleftea"
            ]
          }
        },
        "sektorer": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Sectors",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-skelleftea"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "At present, mainly bolted routes are listed on Sverigeföraren. From right to left.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-skelleftea"
            ]
          }
        },
